# Hand-crafted Wikidata N-Triples fixture for the Phase 118b dump-streaming
# build script (scripts/build_wikidata_index.py). Covers the canonical-
# seven manual-validation set with the entity QIDs verified against
# Wikidata 2026-05 (the original Phase-118 brief had several wrong QIDs:
# Q4093 was Glasgow not Olaf Scholz; Q1124 was Bill Clinton not Friedrich
# Merz; etc.).
#
# Faithful to the production-dump shape: no P279 transitive-closure
# edges (Phase 118b removed the closure walk) and no `wikibase:sitelinks`
# triples (the truthy-dump does not carry them; sitelinks come from
# Pass C SPARQL).
#
# Sort order: lexicographic by subject URI (LC_ALL=C). The streaming
# algorithm in build_wikidata_index.py groups consecutive triples by
# subject and asserts each subject is seen exactly once, so this
# ordering is load-bearing. After edits, sort the data lines with
# `LC_ALL=C grep -v '^#' file.nt | LC_ALL=C sort -u` and check.
#
# Coverage map (entity → bucket(s) → reason):
#   Q64       Berlin                cities_population_threshold P31 Q42744322
#   Q61053    Olaf Scholz           politicians                  P31 Q5 + P106 Q82955
#   Q566257   Friedrich Merz        politicians                  P31 Q5 + P106 Q82955
#   Q567      Angela Merkel         politicians                  P31 Q5 + P106 Q82955
#   Q154797   German Bundestag      government_agencies          P31 Q11204
#   Q313827   Bundesregierung (DE)  government_agencies          P31 Q35798
#   Q162222   Deutsche Bundesbank   central_banks                P31 Q66344
#   Q458      European Union        eu_institutions              qid_any
#
# Negative / out-of-scope controls:
#   Q565    (Wikimedia Commons, P31=Q166118 archives) — must NOT match
#           broadcasters; defends against the Phase 118 relapse trap.
#   Q703907 (Tagesschau, P31=Q15416 TV program)       — out-of-scope:
#           deliberately excluded; "TV program" would flood the index.
#   Q131478 (Der Spiegel, P31=Q41298 magazine)        — out-of-scope:
#           deliberately excluded; "magazine" would flood the index.
#   Q9999   (synthetic noise, P31=Q35120) — must not appear.
